{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation object to add to the receiver. This object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"must conform to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. The map view retains the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation object."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},{"type":"text","text":" objects cannot be added to the map view at this time."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, shape or point collection"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that is specified is silently ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"level":4,"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading"},{"name":"To Do","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Add a line annotation from GeoJSON.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"To Do","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Add an annotation to an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}]}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/addannotation:"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)addAnnotation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1793"},"title":"addAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/addAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the map view."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/addAnnotation:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"title":"addAnnotation:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/addannotation:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Adds an annotation to the map view.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/addAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolyline"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","title":"MLNMultiPolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","title":"MLNPointCollection","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"orchard."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"title":"MLNPolyline","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]}}}